**Substitution Rules**:
- Replace ALL `[REGION]` with detected region name (e.g., "France")
- Replace ALL `[region-code]` with lowercase code (e.g., "fr")
- Replace ALL `[REGION-CODE]` with uppercase code for mission IDs (e.g., "FR" for "FR-E2E-001")
